body: Double trap as in double rape my dude

okay. that is probably the first time I decided to read a Rape Tagged one that actually turned out >hilarious<, instead of horribly stupid or depressing. I genuinely laughed. Not what I was expecting from the title, I was trying to satisfy my curiosity on just what a 'Double Trap' would be, a Trap is already vacuous...are Traps Gay? What then....of Double Traps? Alas, this one shall not answer either.
